        public Result(boolean headerCompleted,
              HttpResponse response,
              boolean requestCompleted,
              boolean overflow,
              boolean underflow)
        Creates a new result.
        Parameters:
        headerCompleted - true if the header has completely been decoded
        response - a response to send due to an error
        requestCompleted - if the result includes a response this flag indicates that no further processing besides sending the response is required
        overflow - true if the data didn't fit in the out buffer
        underflow - true if more data is expected
